Docker Publish DinD (linux/arm64)	UNKNOWN STEP	2026-05-03T20:49:37.3545327Z               "message": "Merge main into issue-524-6aa38eea, take main's version\n\nMain reorganized the helpers and added a different /stop command\n(pause new tasks for chat) which we keep functioning. The previous\nPR's session-tracking and CTRL+C logic in telegram-bot-helpers.lib.mjs,\ntelegram-stop-command.lib.mjs and experiments/test-stop-command.mjs\nhave been dropped — they will be replaced with a UUID-aware extension\nto main's telegram-start-stop-command.lib.mjs that calls $ --stop <UUID>.",
